data.description: Upon Entry Home Offers Formal Dining Room, Den. Spacious Living Room w/ Gas Fireplace, Ceiling Fan. New Updated Gourmet Kitchen w/ Eat-in Area, Granite Countertops, Center Island, Custom Cabinets, Canned Lighting, All Stainless Steel Appliances  Sliding Glass Door off eat in area opens to Stamp Paver Patio, Kid Safe Fully Fenced Yard. Laundry room Main level. Lux Master Suite offers Twin Closets, Full Private Bath, Canned Lighting, Ceiling fan. All remaining Bedroom good size. Home shows great. All has been done for you Home is ready to move in and enjoy.    NEWS / NEWERS INCLUDE Remodeled Kitchen, New Cabinets, Counter Tops, All Stainless Steel Appliances Canned lighting almost the entire home. New Hardwood Flooring Main level of home sharp. Need more space no problem Full Finished Basement w/Full bath Bar, very sharp. Nothing to do but move in enjoy Garbage Disposal 2023. AC & Furnace 2021. Sump Pump 2020. Garage door opener & spring 2023 Basement bar stays.
